  "ifCXr9po8n9tTIivjt4XUH": {
    "role": "editor",
    "value": {
      "createdAt": 1778340551726,
      "createdBy": "144115381524278509",
      "enabled": true,
      "id": "ifCXr9po8n9tTIivjt4XUH",
      "parentId": "E9N3w0zwgvCSR7Z6YU6pp5",
      "parentTable": "block",
      "props": {
        "title": [
          [
            "The video was a cooking tutorial about how to make traditional Chinese New Year dishes, especially dumplings and braised pork. These dishes sound a little difficult at first, but the blogger explained the process in a very clear and engaging way. The video did not just show the recipes. It also taught some basic cooking techniques, which made the whole process much easier to follow.",
            [
              [
                "b"
              ]
            ]
          ]
        ]
      },
      "spaceId": "300000000$NjSNnIQtBabS",
      "type": "text",
      "updatedAt": 1778340582375,
      "updatedBy": "144115381524278509",
      "version": 4
    }
  },
  "jsUp5S61TlsJmKc25Rp0am": {
    "role": "editor",
    "value": {
      "createdAt": 1777699306672,
      "createdBy": "144115381524278509",
      "enabled": true,
      "id": "jsUp5S61TlsJmKc25Rp0am",
      "parentId": "2qXhBHPjMbnZH42Q7YcB8J",
      "parentTable": "block",
      "props": {
        "title": [
          [
            "今年的春节，我决定做个年夜饭",
            [
              [
                "b"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          [
            "(特别场合的食物)",
            [
              [
                "b"
              ],
              [
                "h",
                "red"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          [
            "(组织的快乐活动)",
            [
              [
                "b"
              ],
              [
                "h",
                "rose_red"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          [
            "。我找了一个很受欢迎的美食烘培博主的视频",
            [
              [
                "b"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          [
            "(有趣视频)",
            [
              [
                "b"
              ],
              [
                "h",
                "orange"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          [
            "，教人如何准备精美的饺子和红烧肉，因为这两样菜几乎是我们过春节上必不可少的菜肴，同时也比较简单适合我这种新手，最后拍下了一张照片",
            [
              [
                "b"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          [
            "(微笑的场合)",
            [
              [
                "b"
              ],
              [
                "h",
                "blue"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          [
            "。",
            [
              [
                "b"
              ],
              [
                "h",
                "purple"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          [
            "为了买食材，在春节晚上出行，结果很多人都是这时候回家",
            [
              [
                "b"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          [
            "(交通拥堵) 。",
            [
              [
                "b"
              ],
              [
                "h",
                "green"
              ]
            ]
          ]
        ]
      },
      "spaceId": "300000000$NjSNnIQtBabS",
      "type": "text",
      "updatedAt": 1780209681460,
      "updatedBy": "144115381524278509",
      "version": 48
    }
  },
  "k0lL3U3Dl8YYOFgg9wUqWB": {
    "role": "editor",
    "value": {
      "createdAt": 1777699307413,
      "createdBy": "144115381524278509",
      "enabled": true,
      "id": "k0lL3U3Dl8YYOFgg9wUqWB",
      "parentId": "IrY71auCzaarNS20mLtFIQ",
      "parentTable": "block",
      "props": {
        "title": [
          [
            "串题的串词你可以提前读一下，但是我更建议你在具体的回答中熟悉。因为你直接背串词是碎片的，会很痛苦，而你从故事里面记会更自然，并且你会发现，同样的情节都是用这些话，所以会记忆得更快",
            [
              [
                "b"
              ]
            ]
          ]
        ]
      },
